{"tid":139918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國會演說】特朗普向中產大幅減稅 冀移民法例助就業加人工","createTime":"2017-03-01T20:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T06:27:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5302bff463b8d859ff535f0011618e48f7f88645","tid":139918,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T20:16:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170301&amp;guid=56368608&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170301%26guid%3D56368608%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=20700d05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170301%26guid%3D56368608%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=f4af82fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170301&amp;guid=56368608&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n2017-03-01 10:15:31 HKT  <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170301/large/1488334847_857c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170301%2Flarge%2F1488334847_857c.jpg&h=461bd94a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【新增動新聞】<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普首次在國會兩院聯席會議發表演說，規格如同「國情咨文」（State of the Union），闡述未來一年政府政策，他提出會為中產階層提供「大規模減稅」等，而在公眾聚焦的移民議題，特朗普表示會推行法例協助他們就業並提高工資。<br />\n<br />\n他在演說開首強調要復興美國精神，「我們的盟國會發現美國再次準備好站在領導位置，全球所有國家--無論是友是敵，都會發現美國很強大，美國值得驕傲及美國是自由的。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又再為移民政策辯論，他說：「透過終於落實我們的移民法例，我們有望提高工資，協助失業者，省下數十億美元開支並讓社區對任何人來說都更安全。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普之前曾表示，會提出自列根經濟學以來最大規模的稅務改革。他的演說亦率先披露部份細節，「我的經濟團隊準備推行歷史性的稅務改革，將減輕本土公司的稅率，讓他們可在任何地方都保持競爭力和發展。同時我們會為中產階層提供大規模減稅措施。」<br />\n<br />\n他亦都向前任總統奧巴馬的醫保改革出招，說會致力降低藥價，讓民眾有自主選擇適合自己的醫療保險。他認為，強制美國人去支付政府批准的醫療保險絕非正確方案，而是應降低醫療保險的成本，從而令每個人都能夠負擔才是上策。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/《蘋果》資料室"},{"pid":"7174648f8f180c48c4db3470e1650e6ad953a738","tid":139918,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T22:50:03.000Z","msg":"左膠可能寧願收留多幾個難民都唔要減稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77832985582bcde66710a3119cf62f70ba280a39","tid":139918,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de754ebb30f6a281724641358e52eb10db86a307","tid":139918,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"明明佢既政策合情理咁多就係唔政治正確就比班左膠日屌夜屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95ae6e9d943193b7bfa363d582171551a6f1559","tid":139918,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明佢既政策合情理咁多就係唔政治正確就比班左膠日屌夜屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncut晒d左膠既funding就岩"},{"pid":"a7e44b30d3204c98c6df459691b639efc7bf9a46","tid":139918,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:03:03.000Z","msg":"左翼點解唔支持佢搞福利主義"},{"pid":"a2d0e1ff43a05015aa0a987f2dd6e5c7c12a8426","tid":139918,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:03:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>明明佢既政策合情理咁多就係唔政治正確就比班左膠日屌夜屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncut晒d左膠既funding就岩</blockquote><br />\n封曬果d ngo 逼佢地出黎做野"},{"pid":"aac2b466753ff7124d1921aa808eece1ecd3a673","tid":139918,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:29:11.000Z","msg":"中產減稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae6e52303ecce9816fed999cce4876ac66aa64d","tid":139918,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src